'''氟氯化铅'''是一种[[无机化合物|无机化合物]]，化学式为PbClF，它可由[[氟化铅|氟化铅]]和[[氯化铅|氯化铅]]共熔得到。<ref name=Chen>{{Cite journal|title=Crystal growth of PbFCl by modified Bridgman method|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0022024802023539|last=Chen|first=Jianming|last2=Shen|first2=Dingzhong|date=2003-04-01|journal=Journal of Crystal Growth|issue=3|doi=10.1016/S0022-0248(02)02353-9|volume=250|pages=393–396|language=en|issn=0022-0248|last3=Mao|first3=Rihua|last4=Ren|first4=Guohao|last5=Yin|first5=Zhiwen|access-date=2021-12-16|archive-date=2021-12-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211216064109/https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0022024802023539|dead-url=no}}</ref>它是四方晶系晶体，空间群''P''4/''mmm''。<ref>Pierre Villars,Karin Cenzual,Roman Gladyshevskii. Handbook. pp 350. ISSN 9783110311747.</ref>它在258 nm的紫外光激发下，可以发出紫色荧光（E<sub>m</sub>=391 nm）。<ref name=Chen />

氟氯化铅在自然界中以{{le|氟氯铅矿|Matlockite}}的形式存在。<ref>[http://www.mindat.org/jrs/JRS%20Vol%2001-2.pdf Phosgenite and Matlockite in Derbyshire (Part 1)] {{Wayback|url=http://www.mindat.org/jrs/JRS%20Vol%2001-2.pdf |date=20121110070641 }}, T. Bridges, M.E. Smith, Journal of the Russell Society Volume 1, No. 2, p7-14, 1983 Retrieved on 2011-01-11</ref>它也是一类具有该结构化合物（如CaHBr、PrOCl等）的结构名称。<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Matlockite (PbFCl) Structure|url=https://www.atomic-scale-physics.de/lattice/struk/Matlockite.html|access-date=2021-12-16|work=www.atomic-scale-physics.de}}</ref>
